definitions.definition: A paleocontinent that formed in the Paleoproterozoic and now constitutes northwestern Eurasia , or Europe north of the Trans-European Suture Zone and west of the Ural Mountains.

main_definition: A paleocontinent that formed in the Paleoproterozoic and now constitutes northwestern Eurasia , or Europe north of the Trans-European Suture Zone and west of the Ural Mountains.
